# intersection(_:)

**Instance Method**

Returns a new range set containing the contents of both this set and the given set.

## Declaration

```swift
func intersection(_ other: RangeSet<Bound>) -> RangeSet<Bound>
```

## Parameters

- **other**: The range set to merge with this one.

## Return Value

A new range set.
